* the unperturbed optical transition 6_s_ ^2^S~1/2~ - 4_f_ ^13^6_s_^2^ ^2^stem:["F"]~7/2~ of the ^stem:[171^(Yb)]+^ ion with a frequency of stem:[f]~171Yb+~ (octupole) = stem:[642 121 496 772 645.6 "Hz"] and an estimated relative standard uncertainty of 1.3 × 10^−15^. +
 This radiation is recommended to be endorsed by the CIPM as a secondary representation of the second;
